msgstr ""

#: 03006:1076
msgid ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"Work is important, but family is more important. You work for your family, so if you get lost in work, you're losing sight of what really counts.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1080
msgid ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"Wow, you've actually given this thought.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1081
msgid "The girls liked how he showed his commitment to his future family. They gave Daigo a new, proud look."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1085
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"You're the kind of man who would make his wife very happy.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1089
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"Doesn't sound very interesting to me, but more importantly, I doubt he'd get promoted.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1096
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Of course I'd want my husband to get promotions, but I'd still want him to put his family first. I think Daigo-kun's way of thought is best.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1097
msgid "For the first time, Daigo found himself being a favorite amongst the girls."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1103
msgid ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"Am I getting popular all of a sudden?\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1104
msgid "He was shaking in joy."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1105
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"You sure are! Congratulations, Daigo!\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1108
msgid ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"I can now die a happy man.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1113
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"It's too soon. You should enjoy being popular for a bit longer.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1114
msgid ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"I'm already fulfilled. I'm in the prime of my life right now.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1118
msgid ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"Ahaha... I suddenly feel bad for Daigo.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1123
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Kazushi-kun! How about you?\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1124
msgid "Haruka showed a big interest in what I wanted."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1129
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"Yeah, what's your type? I've got a feeling that you like thrifty girls.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1130
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What makes you think that?\n"
"My type is......\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1131
msgid "My thoughts turned to a vast, broad landscape with plains stretching as far as I could see."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1137
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"If I ever fell in love with a girl, I'd want to go on a journey. I'd get my license, buy a car - even an old, beat up one would do - and take a trip all around Japan or across Eurasia.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1141
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"There'd be a dog with me and the girl I loved. And the three of us would live together, travelling all of Japan or the world.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1142
msgid "I'd always had that dream, but I'd always been too shy to tell anyone else about it. It only slipped because of this situation."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1144
msgid "We'd only just come to this island Academy, but in our classroom, in the middle of the night, sleeping together, I felt something special that made me want to share that dream with everyone tonight."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1150
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"That's so cheesy, Kazushi!!\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1151
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"That cheese is still raw!\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1152
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Shut up!\n"
"Why should you guys care about my dream anyways!?\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1153
msgid "I know it's cheesy. I'm embarrassed."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1158
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"I like your dream. I wanna travel and go where I've never been before. I've never even been off this island yet.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1159
msgid "Haruka looked into the distance. Maybe she was already on a road trip in her mind."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1164
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"That's so romantic, too. You'd be together with the one you loved all morning, afternoon, and night.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1168
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"I dunno, I might get bored halfway through. Though I guess at that point I'd start collecting currency from all the different countries.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1172
msgid ""
"{Andou}\n"
"\"You wouldn't get bored. If you did, then it would mean you weren't with the right person.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1176
msgid ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"Ahaha, Rei-chan, you are such a romantic little girl.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1180
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"I want a car, too. I'm thinking about getting my license as soon as I graduate.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1184
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Me too. I want to go for a long drive with my Fuu-chan.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1188
msgid ""
"{Fuusen}\n"
"\"A small... Yes, I want a mini cooper!\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1192
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"I want a 4-wheel drive. One with the power and strength to go anywhere. I'd like to get my license too.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1196
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"If I were to take a dog on my road trip, I'd want a Maltese.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1203
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"An indoor dog? No, in a situation like that, you go for a hunting dog like a Beagle.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1206
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"I like St. Bernards! They're so huge, I could sleep with one as my pillow!\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1210
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"I want a Chihuahua to cuddle up with!\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1214
msgid ""
"{Andou}\n"
"\"Oh! Me too!\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1218
msgid ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"You'd crush it!\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1222
msgid "We were having way too much fun to fall asleep, and kept on talking about random topics."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1226
msgid "Before we knew it, the scenery outside was getting brighter and the birds were chirping."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1229
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"*Yawn* Is it morning already?\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1234
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Who's still up?\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1241
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"I'm sorry, I fell asleep for a second!\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1242
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No, go ahead and sleep.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1245
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"You did a good job of staying up late with us, considering how you go to bed at ten sharp every night.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1249
msgid ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"I'm sleepy, too. I can barely tell up from down anymore.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1250
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Zzzzz......Zzzzzz......\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1254
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"Rin-chan's been asleep for ages.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1258
msgid ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"So are Appo and Fuusen.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1262
msgid "They were sleeping in each other's arms. Andou was asleep right next to Fuusen."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1263
msgid "There weren't many survivors left."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1264
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Should we go to sleep too?\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1267
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Will we be alright if we fall asleep here now? I don't think I'll be able to wake up again before noon.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1272
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"It'll work out. *Yawn* Back to sleep.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1279
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"Me too. Wake me up when we have to leave.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1283
msgid "One by one, we departed for dreamland. That's when Pierre crawled over next to me."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1286
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"What were we doing being such nice boys? We could have done lots of other pervy things!\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1287
msgid "I didn't even realize that we'd had a chance until Pierre told me so."
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1288
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Oh yeah...you're right.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1293
msgid ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"We always make mistakes when it counts the most. That's why we never get laid.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1294
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"Don't be so hard on yourself.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1295
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Well, this is just the beginning of summer break.\""
msgstr ""

#: 03006:1298
msgid "I have a feeling that this summer is going to be something special for us. One like we've never had before. I wonder what lies in store."
msgstr ""
